title: MTBPS 2015: Government Must Reduce Spending (IFP - Inkatha Freedom Party)
text: ( Source : IFP - Inkatha Freedom Party ) The Inkatha Freedom Party expects the Minister of Finance , Hon. Nhlanhla Nene , to announce measures to reign in government spending during his Medium Term Budget Policy Statement to be delivered
